import { Component, ViewChild } from '@angular/core'; import { NgForm } from '@angular/forms'; @Component({ selector: 'app-register', templateUrl: './register.component.html', styleUrls: ['./register.component.scss'], }) export class RegisterComponent { @ViewChild('profileForm') profileForm!: NgForm; @ViewChild('resumeForm') resumeForm!: NgForm; onSubmit() { const profData = this.profileForm.value; const resumeData = this.resumeForm.value; console.log(`profData: ${profData}`); console.log(`resumeData: ${resumeData}`); } }
